    "alternating_central_term_test": "A central anomaly at this layer must have nonzero alternating part D(a,b)-D(b,a).",
    "canonical_clock_defect": "For the sector-26 clock q on the rank-10 operator basis, D(a,b)=q(a xor b)-q(a)-q(b) mod 26.",
    "compatible_f2_search": "Search alternating F2 forms on unordered named-generator pairs, force zero on pairs with zero sector-26 clock defect, and require descent through C5_9+C5_10+C9_10=0."
